<plot>Three native children visit their grandfather on his trap line where they experience the traditional ways of trapping, hunting and fishing. In their journey they discover that the lack of food in the area may cause their Christmas holidays to be cancelled. The children set off alone to save their Christmas and soon learn that this way of life is not as easy as it seems.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104995</url></doc>
